                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brandOrange font-bold mt-0.5">&rarr;</span> <span><strong>Premium profit model</strong> &mdash; High-wattage 100W+ GaN V charger with retractable cable and digital display for the power user segment</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase text-sm mb-4 tracking-widest">Execution</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Once the product configuration was finalized, we fast-tracked the project with a dedicated production line. Sample turnaround was compressed to <strong>5 days</strong> (vs. standard 15-20). Our supply chain team secured priority allocation for GaN V components, and QC passed all units on the first pass with zero rework required.</p>
