                         width="800" height="600"
                         loading="lazy"
                         decoding="async"
                         class="w-full rounded-[2rem] mb-6 shadow-lg">
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Jacob Jensen&rsquo;s design philosophy extends to every detail, and the packaging was no exception. This was among the most premium packaging we have ever produced. The brief called for a <strong>two-piece rigid gift box</strong> that would convey the product&rsquo;s premium positioning at first touch.</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">The packaging went through <strong>6 rounds of sampling</strong> to perfect every detail: material selection (eco-friendly paper stock), structural integrity, magnetic closure tension, insert molding precision, and print color accuracy. The final result was a package that Jacob Jensen&rsquo;s team approved as matching the quality standards of their watch packaging &mdash; the highest compliment from a brand built on design excellence.</p>
                    <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase text-sm mb-4 tracking-widest">Results</h3>
